Class MoonEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • br.com.henriquewilhelm.orbit.Event
      • br.com.henriquewilhelm.orbit.MoonEvent

  • public class MoonEvent
extends Event
    The class extends of Event class, gathers the calculations of Moon The calculations are:

    Rise and set Time, HorizonToHorizonCrossing type, Time meridianCrossing (noon), Time antimeridianCrossing (Midnigth), Position (rightAscention, declination, longitudeEcliptic and distance)

    Version:
    v1.0.0
    Author:
